      • getEpc

        public TagData getEpc()
        Contains the contents of the tag EPC memory backscatter by the tag. This does not contain the PC or CRC bits.
        Returns:
        the EPC as TagData

      • getAntennaPortNumber

        public short getAntennaPortNumber()
        Returns:
        The antenna port number on which the tag was observed. If the report has coalesced more than one read, this contains the most recent antenna on which the tag was seen.
        See Also:
        ReportConfig.setIncludeAntennaPortNumber(java.lang.Boolean)

        public double getChannelInMhz()

        See Also:

      • getFirstSeenTime

        public ImpinjTimestamp getFirstSeenTime()
        Returns:
        The first time that the tag was seen in this tag report. If the report contains multiple tag observations the first seen time is the earliest time of the observations coalesced to produce this report.
        See Also:
        ReportConfig.setIncludeFirstSeenTime(java.lang.Boolean)

      • setFirstSeenTime

        protected void setFirstSeenTime(ImpinjTimestamp firstSeenTime)

      • getLastSeenTime

        public ImpinjTimestamp getLastSeenTime()
        Returns:
        The last time that the tag was seen in this tag report. If the report contains multiple tag observations the last seen time is the latest time of the observations coalesced to produce this report.
        See Also:
        ReportConfig.setIncludeLastSeenTime(java.lang.Boolean)
